<% provide(:title,'Professionals') %>
<%= render 'layouts/staticbanner' %>

<div class="well">
  <h2>Professionals</h2>
  <p class="lead">Hosting a student has benefits beyond contributing to your local community</p>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-2 col-lg-2">
    <div class="textContainer">
    <p>Professionals involved in the Future Young Professional program are involved in the community, making it a good opportunity to network with other driven individuals.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-2 col-lg-2">
    <div class="ImageContainer">
      <%= image_tag("#{@pagename}1.jpg", :class => "img-rounded", :width => "100%", :height => "100%") %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-2 col-lg-2">
    <div class="textContainer">
      <p>Students can provide an objective insight into your job making it a good opportunity for casual feedback and input.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-2 col-lg-2">
    <div class="ImageContainer">
    <%= image_tag("#{@pagename}2.jpg", :class => "img-rounded", :width => "100%", :height => "100%") %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-2 col-lg-2">
    <div class="textContainer">
      <p>Hosting a student at your job demonstrates to your peers that you are committted to volunteering and your community.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-2 col-lg-2">
    <div class="ImageContainer">
    <%= image_tag("#{@pagename}3.jpg", :class => "img-rounded", :width => "100%", :height => "100%") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

